"First, what is the difference between the Unified Force and God?"The OT, NT, and the body of Christian Theology.It did not create man out of clay, build a garden, drown everyone, part the Red Sea, send it's only son..."Second, what caused the Unified Force to break itself apart?"The cooling / expanding universe.The unified force did not create anything, it was just the force that acted on matter before the universe cooled to the point that it decayed.